{"hac1a90b4g591eg46bcg95d7g30000d95e074": ["Stop! I give up! M-mercy, please!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "bf5c6a98-7122-354d-cd26-083c58343f39"], "hc535deb6gc397g4b05ga304g306e06be291c": ["I know things. If you let me live, I'll make it worth your while. I p-promise!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "eea6b616-9a14-fe00-d93a-da3a81a1fecf"], "hfa87af0cgaa92g4f80g94d8g0c52a2ea1152": ["I want the gold you took. Now.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "b357f1ee-5447-acef-04a1-4010310efa76"], "hefdf5292gdc69g489cgb811g579aab5f6f0f": ["A-all right, fine. Take it - take it all! Now... can I go...?", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "3dd38436-f719-7885-3b4e-a5bf9f3ad145"], "h57510071g91a2g4b02gb859g1f189fa472c6": ["A-all right, fine. Take it - take... wait. It's... it's gone!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "a9e893d1-b83a-6acb-a4a0-907883c6ac8f"], "hb189feb8gf947g4573ga1b1gbd863e1dadec": ["Talk and you might live. <i>If</i> it's worth my while.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "b349e436-0512-859f-a843-b57a810c3095"], "h5aab27a1gc452g4007gbeb9g56033e1541d8": ["M-my lot are camped nearby - I can get you inside, no hassle! You can loot it, do whatever!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "b7db0d30-fb93-5fec-165a-b52ea9124ce4"], "h8970219bg33d0g442cga28bg77c64cc9ab3e": ["There's a hidden path, p-past the bridge into the camp. Over to the side before you reach the first guards. Easy.", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "4e741dbb-17df-4ab9-731a-c7f206befd36"], "h3cc85c60g0066g4d5fg9e17g029b1676d257": ["Run along, goblin. Before I change my mind.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "f9cd5681-c835-c90c-70d8-e303ce01c304"], "hf37a998eg47a8g4ca5g96fdg046683916dc3": ["T-thanks!  And 'pologies. And... erm... bye!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "669fd0f5-b128-496a-57ce-31ee2ca07e6b"], "hcf4d45bdg5eb9g4f3fg8aedg2644c1904ebc": ["You're staying right here - my companion, Wyll, wants a word.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "c9adb1cb-9550-7a5a-8be9-46c07857fd9c"], "h54adf322g6d0ag4e80g9c78gd516b0cc7bf7": ["A word...? Alright, w-what you say...", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "cad54026-8547-dd87-10f0-3eb02ec2a3bd"], "h9c9f6f4fg1fbdg4ebdgae51gfcac1351d3ba": ["<i>No mercy. Kill the goblin.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "04adc43d-0f4d-b7be-5064-5c44a65173a5"], "h8ad12a5bgde6fg451bg9b59gf9aac88fc8b5": ["No, wait!", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "11d45007-3cde-9aa2-6c73-7ec93ad9905a"], "h1b2dda60g5225g4e0egb525g1b4b9f9086a9": ["You sure I c-can't just leave?", "b2c582af-bc69-48b3-a004-648562dab404", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "2482deee-85c4-eb5c-49bd-8f10903bf10c"], "h10fd7223g5e85g45f2gae4bg1aadf8d991a6": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Forest\\FOR_GnomeGoblin1_Surrender_NotAtWindmill.html", "0b329bb4-4c31-be72-323e-5c74443b9960"]}